### 4.4 RBN Push Relay ✅ COMPLETE & DEPLOYED
- [x] RBN stores push tokens for connected peers
- [x] When message stored in mailbox, RBN sends FCM push
- [x] Push payload: `{device_type, token, peer_id_hash}` (minimal, encrypted)
- [x] Actual message content stays encrypted in mailbox
- [x] Fallback to mesh delivery if push fails
- [x] Deployed to `root@47.89.252.80` on 2026-06-16

### 4.5 Background Sync Optimization ✅ COMPLETE & DEPLOYED
- [x] Removed heartbeat timer (was 10s)
- [x] Increased mailbox_fetch from 30s → 2min
- [x] Increased contact_refresh from 30s → 2min
- [x] Increased status_check from 15s → 60s
- [x] Drive tab refresh from 5s → 30s
- [x] Deployed to RBN on 2026-06-16

### 4.6 Expected Impact
- Battery drain: ~3-5%/hour → ~0.5-1%/hour
- Message delivery: 0-30s → 0-2s (when push available)
- CPU wakeups: ~10,000/day → ~500-1,000/day
- Samsung Deep Sleep: survives vs gets killed

